sentences: Billie Jean Jones Eshleman Williams Horton Berlin (born June 6, 1933), professionally known as Billie Jean Horton, is an American country-music singer-songwriter and former music promoter who is best known for her high profile marriages, firstly to iconic country musician and singer-songwriter Hank Williams Sr.
